    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Upload an Image\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help plan ideas for improving the playground.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. **Write a prompt** that asks AI Chat to suggest some improvements to a playground. In your prompt, describe some features of a typical playground. *Don't have a prompt? That's ok! You can copy one from below the instructions.*\r\n3. Press **Send**.\r\n4. **Attach an image** of a playground from the Library to your prompt.\r\n5. **Write a prompt** that asks AI Chat for help improving the playground in the picture you've attached.\r\n3. Press **Send**.\r\n5. Then read and compare **AI Chat's responses**.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-file-image-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I upload an image?**]\r\n- Click the button labeled **Upload** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Library**\r\n- Then browse the existing images.\r\n- When you have an image to upload, click the checkbox next to it to select it and then click **Open**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need a starting prompt?**]\r\n>I’m a Parks and Rec working looking for a project to improve a playground with swings, slides, and benches. What are some ideas?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n",
